HotelButler

agents:
	humans: Guest
	robots: Butler
locations: lobby, room1, room2
resources: item1, item2

Butler:

1-5: stop until position(Butler, lobby)
6-7: moveTo lobby
8-9: checkPINCode(item2)
10: deliver(item2, room1)

Guest:

10-15: enterPINCode(item1)
16: take(item1)

Butler:

10-15: moveTo Guest
16: skip if !isNeeded(item1) && weight(item2) < th
17: collaborativeGrasping(item2)
18: deliver(item2, room1)
